Tigerhawk/Starwind/Silverbolt



Tigerhawk open a com to all the maximals at the battle of the 
cf. "This is tigerhawk the enemy is retreating. Only attack the ones 
not leaving." Tigerhawk fired 12 rounds of bullets at Unitron.






~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Starwind fired the three front lazer cannons at Unitron.


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Silverbolt fired two missles at Unitron.
